commentary: Richardson to Jadhav, OUT taken at deep midwicket! There goes India's final hope, trying to pull a short ball that is a touch too close to the body for him to get any power, and just a little too much bounce for him to deal with. Tiny bit of a top edge and Maxwell on the boundary does some great work, running to his right and taking a clean catch at high pressure. Australia have been pushed to their very limit in this series, but they've found heroes every single time

commentary: Stoinis to Kuldeep Yadav, OUT flattens the middle stump to end a sensational tour! Australia won the T20Is 2-0, and now they come back from 0-2 down to win the ODI series 3-2. Australia's first ODI series win in India since 2009. What a win, what a performance. Massive injection of confidence ahead of the World Cup. Only four times in ODI history has a team come back from 0-2 down to win a five-match series. Australia are the fifth side. What an achievement!
